    <item>
      <title>About Me</title>
      <link>https://grafmaxi.github.io/maximilian-graf/about/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://grafmaxi.github.io/maximilian-graf/about/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Since 2022, I have been a PhD student at the University of Potsdam, supervised by &lt;a href=&#34;https://sites.google.com/site/alexandracarpentierresearch/home&#34;&gt;Alexandra Carpentier&lt;/a&gt; (University of Potsdam) and &lt;a href=&#34;https://verzelen.montpellier.inrae.fr&#34;&gt;Nicolas Verzelen&lt;/a&gt; (INRAE Montpellier). My work is funded by the DFG Research Unit &lt;a href=&#34;https://for5381.uni-freiburg.de&#34;&gt;FOR 5381&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;My research interests lie in mathematical statistics and the mathematics underlying machine learning. In particular, I focus on various aspects of unsupervised learning. So far, I have worked on ranking problems in crowdsourcing and clustering in bandit settings.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
